SERVER ASSIGNMENTS

This screen displays the database and CDDS assignments for a Replicator
Server.

The columns on the list are:

        COLUMN NAME     DESCRIPTION
        -----------     -----------
        DB No           The number of a database to which the server
                        transmits.

        Database Name   The database's virtual node and name.

        CDDS            The CDDS number on the database to which the
                        server transmits.

        CDDS Name       The CDDS name.

        Target Type     The target type for the CDDS at the given
                        database.


The menu commands are as follows:

        MENU COMMAND    SYNOPSIS
        ------------    --------
        Help            Access the Help facility.

        End             Return to the Replication Monitor screen.
